import React from 'react'

const Form = () => {
  return (
    <><form
    // action="https://formspree.io/f/xgedgjkr"
    method="POST"
    // className="contact-inputs"
    >
    <input
      type="text"
      name="username"
      placeholder="username"
      autoComplete="off"
      required
    />

    <input
      type="email"
      name="Email"
      placeholder="Email"
      autoComplete="off"
      required
    />

    <textarea
      name="message"
      cols="30"
      rows="6"
      autoComplete="off"
      required></textarea>

    <input type="submit" value="send" />
  </form>
  </>
  )
}

export default Form
